Greensting Slayer			KEY:Magus Archetype ~ Greensting Slayer					CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.MagusArchetype.MagusArmorProficiency										PRECLASS:1,Magus=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Magus Archetype ~ Greensting Slayer],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,TYPE.MagusArmorProficiency]																DESCISPI:YES	DESC:The blending of martial prowess with elven magic has long been a staple of the Blackash Training Grounds in Erages. More than a few who study at Erages Academy follow this path because of the promises of wealth that the city's criminal element makes toward practiced brawlers and smugglers.																																																				ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Greensting Slayer ~ Arcane Pool	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Evasion|PRECLASS:1,Magus=7	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Improved Evasion|PRECLASS:1,Magus=13																																		COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.9	ASPECT:Archetype Base Class|Magus
Arcane Pool				KEY:Greensting Slayer ~ Arcane Pool						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural																																																											DESC:You can expend 1 point from your arcane pool as a swift action to add %2d6 points of sneak attack damage to your next melee attack this round. The attack must meet all of the usual prerequisites for making a sneak attack, as the rogue class feature. If you get a sneak attack from another source, the bonuses on damage stack.|1+min(4,floor((MagusLVL-1)/4))																																																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.9

