Masterpiece (The Canticle of Joy)	KEY:Masterpiece ~ The Canticle of Joy			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.Masterpiece			SOURCEPAGE:p.27		DESC:This agonizing eulogy gets into a listener's blood, and bestows on him the phantom sensation of all the agonies suffered by Zon-Kuthon's most pious worshipers. One target within range is cursed as though affected by bestow curse as long as the bard maintains the performance. Although this lullaby does have words, it is not a language-dependent effect. Use: 1 bardic performance round per round. Action: 1 round.
